1.1.1.1
log
@Import p5-URI-Find.   

This module does one thing: Finds URIs and URLs in plain text. It    
finds them quickly and it finds them all (or what URI::URL considers    
a URI to be.)    

From Jasper Lievisse Adriaanse <jasper at nedbsd.nl>.
@
